335
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,280
- Tchau.
- Tchau.

336
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:55,560
- Toda vez.
- Toda vez.

337
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,880
- Tchau!
- Tchau.

338
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,240
Tchau.

339
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:40,160
